column2: SELECT TOP #  p.specobjid,p.ra,p.dec,p.z, g.best_model_z as metallicity, s.oii_#_flux,s.oii_#_flux_err,s.oii_#_flux,s.oii_#_flux_err,s.h_alpha_flux,s.h_alpha_flux_err,s.h_beta_flux,s.h_beta_flux_err,s.oiii_#_flux,s.oiii_#_flux_err,s.oiii_#_flux,s.oiii_#_flux_err,s.nii_#_flux,s.nii_#_flux_err,s.nii_#_flux,s.nii_#_flux_err, m.mstellar_median, m.mstellar_err,m.warning as bc0#warn FROM galSpecInfo AS p  JOIN galSpecLine AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid  JOIN galSpecIndx as g ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# as m ON s.specobjid = m.specobjid WHERE   p.z BETWEEN # AND #
